high_descs: Turn around and move to the front of the stove.
Pick up the pan on the back right burner.
Turn and walk to the sink
Place the pan in the sink and turn the water on then off.
Move back to the front of the stove.
Place the pan on the front right burner on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Move a rinsed pan from one burner to another.

high_descs: Go left, and then left again to stand in front of the stove.
Pick the pan up from the right of the stove.
Turn around and stand in front of the sink.
Put the pot in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then take the pot out of the sink.
Go left to stand in front of the stove.
Put the pot down on the bottom right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on the stove.

high_descs: turn left and walk to the fridge, then turn left and walk to the stove on the left
grab a dirty sauce pan off of the back right burner of the stove
turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink on the right
place the pan inside the sink to clean it off, then take it out once it is clean
turn around and walk back over to the stove on the right
place the pan down on the front right burner
anns.task_desc: place a clean sauce pan down on the front right burner
